<p>Here‚Äôs the deal:</p>

<p>You want to know which CPU is best to pair with the GTX 1070.</p>

<p>In this article, we‚Äôre going to talk about three terrific options - but before that, you need to know the following:</p>

<p>There is no such thing as the ‚Äúbest CPU‚Äù, only the best CPU for you and your needs.</p>

<p>With that being said, the following three CPUs are the best choices for the GTX 1070 from a performance per dollar standpoint.</p>

<p>They‚Äôre all powerful enough to easily keep pace with the GTX 1070, avoiding bottlenecks and helping you game at peak performance.</p>

<p>With that being said, let‚Äôs take a look at the best CPUs for the GTX 1070:</p>

